entries.journal_entry_description: CaptainTypho has asked for help with the local police force as they are currently undermanned.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Doogal Belstar is one of the most wanted men on Naboo. Find one of his men who has information about his location. The Mauler Apprentices are probably the best bet. Kill them until you discover his location.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: That was exactly what we expected. One of the Mauler Disciples had a map. We're uploading the coordinates to your datapad. Go check it out and see if you can find Doogal.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: One of the disciples had a map to a location on Naboo. I'm going to go there and see if Doogal is anywhere nearby.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I need to speak with Officer Nok
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Officer Nok said that Doogal was seen doing something near the grave marker at this location. I should search it and see if there's anything there.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: The concealed package mentions the meeting point for Doogal and his troops. Go there and take care of him before he gears up!
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: The package contained information on where I can find Doogal Belstar. I should go and take care of him.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Return to Typho to finish up this task.
